General.Name: Greater Than AB
General.Description: Greater Than AB provides cloud-based real-time analysis of accident risk and software solutions for the automotive and insurance industries in Sweden. Its products include Enerfy AI - data mining and pattern profiling; and Enerfy risk portfolio tracker. The company offers its solutions for insurance, fleet, mobility, and automotive industries. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
